<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="interest-n">interest <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɪntrəst/    美 /'ɪntrəst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>兴趣：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have / develop an interest in</strong>
对…产生兴趣</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>show / lose interest in</strong> 
对…表现出/失去兴趣</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>took an interest in</strong> sports. 
他对体育运动感兴趣。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>吸引力；趣味：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His books <strong>are of no interest</strong> to me at all. 
我对他的书毫无兴趣。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are many <strong>places of interest</strong> in the city of Rome.
罗马城有很多名胜古迹。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[常用复数]兴趣爱好：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His two great interests in life are music and chess.
他生活中的两大乐趣是听音乐和下国际象棋。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>利息：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>interest rates</strong>
(银行贷款或存款的)利率</p></div>

<h4 id="5c-u">5.<strong>[C] &amp; [U] [常用复数] 利益：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Make decisions <strong>in the best interests of</strong> (= be the best thing for) their own.
作对他们最有利的决定。</p><footer>2016 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The far side of the moon is of particular<strong><em>_</em></strong>_(interesting)to scientists because it has a lot of deep craters(环形山).  （2020全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. interest  </p></div>